# Power/Lock management
bindsym $mod+Ctrl+Escape exec reboot
bindsym $mod+Escape exec swaylock -f -c 000000
bindsym $mod+Shift+Escape exec systemctl suspend
bindsym $mod+Shift+Ctrl+Escape exec systemctl poweroff

# kill current window
bindsym $mod+w kill

# Quick launch common applications
bindsym $mod+Return exec $term
bindsym $mod+Space exec $menu
bindsym $mod+m exec $music
bindsym $mod+b exec $browser
bindsym $mod+f exec $fileManager
